src: singakhona futsi sitawusebenta ngemandla kute sicedze kucishwa kwagezi vukuzenzele unnamed kulamaviki lamba lwa lengcile, ku cishwa kwakhulu kwagezi ngenhloso yekuwonga kutsikamete u mnotfo wetfu futsi kwa banga bulukhuni lobu khulu kubantfu bonkhe baseningizimu afrika.
tgt: hi nga swi kota naswona hi ta endla swo tala ku herisa ku timiwa ka gezi vukuzenzele unnamed eka mavhiki ma nga ri mangani lama nga hundza, ku timiwa ka gezi ko hlaya ku kavanyetile ikhonomi ya hina no vanga ku tike riwa lokukulu eka ma afrikadzonga hinkwa wo.

src: sigaba se6 sekucishwa kwagezi ngenhloso yekuwonga kwabangelwa kulahleka kwemamegawatts (emamw) langetulu kwe18 000 emandla ekuphehla ngenca yekwephuka kwemayunithi kanye nesiteleka sebasebenti bakaeskom lesingekho emtsetfweni.
tgt: xiteji xa 6 xo timiwa ka gezi xi vangiwile hi ku lahlekeriwa ko tlula kwalomu ka 18 000 wa megawati (mv) ta vuswikoti byo endla gezi hikwalaho ka ku onhaka ka yuniti na xitereke xo ka xi nga hlayisekangi hi vatirhi va eskom.

src: ngemuva kweminyaka lelishumi kunekushoda kwagezi, bantfu baseningizimu afrika bafanele kutfukutsela nekukhatsateka.
tgt: endzhaku ka ku tlula malembe ya khume ya nkayivelo wa gezi, maafrikadzonga va fanerile ku vilela no kwata.

src: ngetikhatsi letifanana naleti, kuvakala shengatsi lentfo ngeke ite iphele nyalo nanyalo.
tgt: hi mikarhi yo fana na leyi, swi twala wonge a ku na ku tikomba ku swi ta fika emakumu.

src: nanome kucishwa kwagezi ngenhloso yekuwonga kubonakala shengatsi sekubi kakhulu, liciniso litsi sesitsatse tincumo letinyenti naletibalulekile tekulungisa lokushoda kwekuphakelwa kwagezi.
tgt: kambe loko ku timiwa ka gezi ku languteka ku ya ku tika, ntiyiso hileswaku se hi tekile magoza ya nkoka yo hlaya ku lwisana na nkayivelo wa mphakelo wa gezi.

src: lesikubeke embili lesitawucala ngako kutsi sikwente, kusimamisa luhlelo lwekuphakelwa kwagezi.
tgt: leswi hi swi rhangisaka emahlweni hi xihatla i ku lawula sisiteme ya gezi.

src: njengaloku loluhlelo seluvuka nekuphehlwa kwagezi sekubuyela esimeni, eskom utawukhona kutsi anciphise kucishwa kwagezi ngenhloso yekuwonga kube setigabeni letiphasi.
tgt: loko sisiteme yi tshamiseka na vuswikoti byo endla gezi byi vuyela evutshan’wini, eskom yi ta kota ku hunguta ku timiwa ka gezi ku ya eka switeji swa le hansi.

src: lesivumelwane lokufinyelelwe kuso emkhatsini waeskom netinyonyana tebasebenti sitakwenta kutsi kukhonwe kulungisa loko lokumcoka kanye nekubuyisela esimeni kusebenta kwemayunithi langentiwe.
tgt: ntwanano lowu nga fikeleriwa exikarhi ka eskom na mihlangano yo yimela va vatirhi wu ta pfumelela ku lunghisa ka nkoka no vuyelerisa ku tirha ka tiyuniti to engetela.

src: kuhanjiswa kwagezi lokusuka ecohora bassa emazambiki sekubuyiselwe esimeni futsi, lokwenta kutsi kungenteke 600 mw kugridi kanye neyunithi ye6 yasemedupi seyiyasebenta kusukela ngemgcibelo, lokukwengete lamanye ema720 mw.
tgt: layini yo fambisa gezi ku suka ecahora bassa emozambique yi vuyele ematshan’wini, yi engetela 600 mw eka giridi, na yuniti ya 6 ya le medupi yi vuyelerile eku tirheni hi mugqivela, leswi nga engetela timegawati tin’wana ta 720. tiyuniti to engetela ti languteriwa ku vuyelela eku tirheni, leswi nga ta ya emahlweni swi hunguta nkayivelo wa nkarhi wa sweswi.

src: emayunithi langentiwe kulindzeleke kutsi asebente futsi, lokuyintfo letakwehlisa kakhulu umtfwalo wekushoda kwagezi lokukhona kwanyalo.
tgt: hi nkarhi wu ri wun’we, swiyenge swa vahlayisi va nawu swi le ku tirheni hi matimba ku lwisa nkavanyeto, vukhamba na vuxisi eka eskom ku lulamisa nxungeto lowu migingiriko ya vugevenga wu nga na yona eka sisiteme ya gezi.

src: ekugcineni, lokumcoka kutsi sidzinga kutsi singete kakhulu likhono lekwenta kugridi.
tgt: ekuheteleni, xa nkoka hi leswaku hi lava ku engetela matirhelo ya giridi.

src: loku kutawudala kutsi eskom akhone kutsi atfole litfuba lekugcineka asesimeni lesibalulekile lesisebentako kanye nekwandzisa kwetsembeka kwetisetjentiswa takhe.
tgt: leswi swi ta nyika eskom nkarhi wo endla ku lunghisa ka nkoka no tlakusa ku tshembela eka switirho swa yona.

src: loko kutawuphindza futsi kwakhe sivikelo sekutsi nanome emayunithi lamanyenti angephuka ngesikhatsi sinye, leminye imitfombolusito ingasetjentiswa.
tgt: swi ta tlhela swi va xisirhelelo leswaku na loko tiyuniti to tala ti onhaka hi nkarhi wun’we, ku nga tirhisiwa tindhawu letin’wana.

src: lesinye setinyatselo lengasitsatsa ngemnyaka wa2018 kwaba kuvusetela luhlelo lwekutsenga emandla lavusetelelwako.
tgt: rin’wana ra magoza yo sungula lawa ndzi nga ya teka hi 2018 a ku ri ku pfuxeta nongonoko wa makumelo ya eneji leyi pfuxetekaka.

src: kwengeta kulokutsengwa kwemandla lamasha ekuphehla ngekusebentisa loluhlelo, kwenyuka kwemkhawulo wemvume yemiklamo yekuphehla kwafinyelela kuma100 mw kusho kutsi batjalitimali labatimele imvume kute bakhe tisetjentiswa kute tifinyelele kulobungaka.
tgt: ku engetela eka makumelo ya xivandla lexintshwa xa vuswikoti byo endla gezi hi ku tirhisa nongonoko lowu, ntlakuso wa xikalo xa layisense xa tiphurojeke letintshwa to endla gezi ku ya 100 mw swi vula leswaku vavekisi va le xihundleni a va lavi layisense ku aka switirhisiwa swo endla gezi ku fika eka sayizi leyi.

src: letingucuko letilula tivule emandla lamakhulu labegcinekile letako elutjalomali.
tgt: ku cinca loku ko olova ku pfurile tindlela to tala ta ku koteka ka vuvekisi.

src: eskom wente kutsi kube nemhlaba edvute netiteshi takhe temandla kute kutsi kube nelutjalomali lolutimele kumiklamo yemandla lavusetelelwako.
tgt: eskom yi endlile leswaku ku va na misava ekusuhi na switichi swa gezi leswi nga kona leyi nga ta tirhisiwa hi vuvekisi bya le xihundleni eka tiphurojeke ta eneji leyi pfuxetekaka.

src: tindlela temadizayini setivele tiphotfuliwe kute kutsi kwentiwe ncono kusebenta kwemayunithi 1, 2 na3 asemedupi kantsi asachubeka kumayunithi 5 na6.
tgt: ku cinciwa ka swivumbeko swi herile ku endlela ku antswisa matirhelo ya tiyuniti ta 1, 2 na 3 ta le medupi naswona swi ya mahlweni eka tiyuniti ta 5 na 6. loko migingiriko leyi yi ri na nkoka naswona yi ta tswala mihandzu eka tin’hweti leti taka, swi le rivaleni leswaku a yi ringanelanga ku ololoxa xiphiqo lexi hi nga langutana na xona.

src: nanome lolokwentiwako kubalulekile futsi kutawutsela titselo kuletinyanga letitako, akukaneli kutsi kulungiseke lenkinga lesibukene nayo.
tgt: leswi mavhiki ma nga ri mangani lama nga hundza ya swi kombiseke hileswaku hi fanele ku endla swo tala no swi endla hi xihatla lexikulu.

src: lokukhonjiswe ngulamaviki lambalwa lengcile kutsi sidzinga kutsi sente kakhulu futsi loko sikwente ngekuphutfuma.
tgt: a ku na xivangelo xa leswaku hikokwalahokayini tiko ro fana na ra hina– ra vuswikoti, matimba na switirhisiwa leswi hi nga na swona – ri fanele ku tiyisela ku vava ka nkayivelo wa gezi.

src: kulamaviki lengcile, besisebenta netindvuna letifanele kanye netikhulu mayelana netinyatselo letengetiwe kutsi sente ngekushesha yonkhe imitamo yekutsi sandzise kuphakelwa kwetfu kwagezi.
tgt: eka mavhiki ma nga ri mangani, a hi ri ku tirheni na vaholobye lava faneleke na vaofisarankulu eka magoza yo hambana yo engetela ku hatlisisa matshalatshala hinkwawo ku tlakusa mphakelo wa hina wa gezi.

src: umlayeto uyacaca: lesi akusiso sikhatsi sekusebenta njengalokwetayelekile.
tgt: hungu ri le rivaleni: lowu a hi nkarhi wo tirha tanihi ntolovelo.

src: nga2020, sasungula sikhungo ifusion centre lesimkhakhaminyenti saba sikhungo sekusebentela kute kutsi kubukwane nemacala ebugebengu lahamba embili, kufaka ekhatsi inkhohlakalo.
tgt: hi 2020, hi tumbuluxile senthara yo hlanganisa ya marhavinyingi tanihi xivindzi xa matirhelo ku ti rhana na vugevenga bya swa timali, ku katsa na vukungu ndzwana.

src: lesikhungo sihlanganisa emakhono ekuphenya etinhlaka tahulumende tekuvimbela bugebengu kanye netekuphepha kanye nalawo esikhungo sebunhloli kutetimali, lesi tfutfukisa tebunhloli kute kutsi tikhungo temtsetfo tiyisebentise eluphenyweni lwato.
tgt: senthara leyi yi hlanganisa vuswikoti bya vulavisisi bya swivumbeko swo sivela vugevenga na swa vusirheleri swa mfumo na leswiya swa senthara ya vunhlori bya timali, leyi tumbuluxaka vunhlori bya tiejensi to hlayisa nawu ku va ti byi tirhisa eka vulavisisi bya tona.

src: eminyakeni lemibili kusukela kwasungulwa ifusion centre , indlela yaso lemkhakhaminyenti ‘yekulandzela imali’ ibe nemiphumela lemihle lemikhulu kakhulu.
tgt: malembe mambirhi kusu kela loko ku tumbuluxiwile senthara yo hlanganisa, endlelo ra yona ra marhavi nyingi ra ku ‘landzelela mali’ ri tswarile mihandzu yo tivikana.

src: kulomnyakatimali lophe lile, umsebenti wefusion centre usekele luphenyo lwenkhohlakalo neku khwabanisa lolunge276.
tgt: eka lembeximali leri nga hundza, ntirho wa senthara yo hlanganisa wu seketerile vulavisisi bya 276 bya vu mbabva na vukungundzwa na.

src: tigidzi letilinganiselwa kuletinger659 tabuyi selwa kuhulumende ngekusebentisa kulondvo lota nekuvumbulula inzuzo yebugebengu.
tgt: kwalomu ka r659 wa timiliyoni ti vuyiseriwile eka mfumo hi ku tirhisa ku hla yisa na ku vuyisela rifuwo leri nga kumiwa hi vuge venga.

src: kulinganiselwa kutigidzi letinger613 letavalwa lekusolwa kutsi tinzuzo tebugebengu.
tgt: kwalomu ka r613 wa timiliyoni ta rifuwo leri ku ehleketeriwaka leswaku ri kumiwile hi vugevenga ti yimisiwile ku tirhisiwa.

src: ifusion centre ekucaleni kwayo yasungulelwa kuphenya inkhohlakalo lephatselene nekutsengwa kwetintfo tecovid19 .
tgt: ekusunguleni, senthara yo hlanganisa a yi tumbu luxiwile hi xikongomelo xo lavisisa vukungundzwana hi mayelana na maxavelo ya leswi fambelanaka na covid19 .

src: manje umsebenti wayo sewukhulisiwe kute kutsi ufake ekhatsi kuphenya kushushunjiswa kwemali, kukhwabanisa, kulawula budlabha, kwesekela nge timali emaphekula kanye nalamanye emacala ebuge bengu labucayi.
tgt: sweswi xileri soximfumo xa yona xi le ku ndlandlamuxiweni ku katsa ku tumbetiwa ka swihlovo swa mali, vumbabva, mafambiselo yo biha, ku hakelela vutherorisi na milandzu ya timali yin’wana yo tivikana.

src: emahawks asandza kwendlala letinye tinchube kelembili letentiwe licembu lelilwa nenkhohlakalo, ifusion centre lebe yincenye yako.
tgt: hawks ya ha ku andlala kun’wana ka ku humelela loku nga endliwa hi xipano xa xintirhwana xo lwisana na vukungundzwana, lexi senthara yo hlanganisa yi nga xiphemu xa xona.

src: emkhatsini wemnya katimali wanga2019 nanga2022, kuboshwe basolwa labange554 baboshelwa inkhohlakalo, kwatsi laba142 babo balahlwa licala.
tgt: exikarhi ka malembeximali ya 2019 na 2022, vaehlekete leriwa va 554 va khomiwile hikwalaho ka vukungu ndzwana, laha 142 va nga voniwa nandzu.

src: lelinye lithulusi lebunhloli lelibalulekile kulucwa ningo lwendlela yekuphila lolwentiwe luphiko lwe kugcogcwa kwemtselo lwaseningizimu (yisars).
tgt: xitirho xa vunhlori bya timali xa nkoka xin’wana i tioditi ta hanyelo leti endli waka hi vukorhokeri bya xibalo bya afrikadzonga (sars).

src: kulomnyaka lophelile, isars iphotfule lucwa ningo lwendlela yekuphila lolunge25 lolowenta tigidzi letinger450 kusombulula emagebe emkhatsini wemali lengenako ledzalulwako nendlela yekuphila yemuntfu.
tgt: lembe leri nga hundza, sars yi hetile 25 wa tioditi ta hanyelo ta kufika eka nkoka wo tlula r450 wa timiliyoni ku ololoxa ku hambana exikarhi ka mali nghena leyi paluxiweke na hanyelo ra munhu.

src: kuyacaca kutsi letinyatselo letitsetfwe ngulolulawulo kubuyisela emandla, likhono nekuncomeka kwetikhungo letilwa nekhohlakalo tinemphu mela lobonakalako lomuhle kakhulu.

src: timali tahulumende letaphangwa tabese tihanjiswa ngaletinye tindlela tiyavunjululwa kantsi futsi labo labatsintse kako mayelana naleto tento bashushiswa tinkantolo.

src: caphela timphawu letisheshe tivele tamdlavuta wasebuntfwaneni more matshediso kungacapheli mdlavuta wase buntfwaneni kanye netinkhomba tawo kusho kutsi bantfwana labanyenti baseningizimu afrika ngesikhatsi batfolakala kutsi banalesifo sisuke sesisezi ngeni leliphakeme.
tgt: xiyaxiya swikoweto swo sungula swa mfukuzana ya vutsongwana more matshediso ku pfumaleka ka vulemukisi bya mfukuzana ya vutsongwana na swikombeto swa yona swi vula leswaku vana va laha afrikadzonga vo tala fembiwa loko vuvabyi se byi ri eka xiyimo xo tika.

src: uma ngabe mdlavuta usheshe watfolakala wabese uyelashwa, ematfuba ekwelulama ngalokuphelele abasetulu.

src: umchumanisi wenhlangano yaseningi zimu afrika yamdlavuta wasebuntfwaneni (ichoc) taryn seegers utsi ngekwati timphawu tamdlavuta kubantfu labancane, unga sita usindzise imphilo.
tgt: taryn seegers, mukondle teri wa vuhlanganisi eka childhood cancer foundation south africa (choc) u vula leswaku hi ku tiva swikoweto swa ntolovelo swa mfuku zana eka vantshwa, u nga pfuna ku ponisa vutomi.

src: "timphawu netinkhomba kungaba matima kutibona emkhatsini wemaguludla, imitfubulela, timila kanye nekuntjintjantjintja kwemiva.
tgt: "swikoweto na swikombeto swi nga nonoha ku swi vona exikarhi ka matshumba ya ntolovelo, mafelangati, ku kula hi xihatla na ku cinca ka swipfukela.

src: nanoma kunjalo, kutfolakala kwato kubalule kile kakhulu," kusho yena.
tgt: hambiswiri tano, ku yi thumba ka ha ri ekusunguleni i swa nkoka," a vula.

src: ngekuya kwenhlangano yaseningizimu afrika yetamdlavuta (icansa), njalo ngemnyaka bantfwana baseningizimu afrika labatfolakala banamdla vuta basemkhatsini walabange800 kuya kulaba 1 000. nanoma kunjalo, lenhlangano ilinganisela ekutsini ihhafu yalaba ntfwana eningizimu afrika abatfolwa.
tgt: ku ya hi cancer association of south africa (cansa), exi karhi ka 800 na 1 000 wa vana va laha afrikadzonga va kumiwa va ri na mfukuzana lembe rin’wana na rin’wana.

src: kwenta siciniseko sekutsi mdlavuta ubonwa masinyane, ichoc yenta tinhlelo tekucaphelisa emimangweni, itjela batali nebantfwana ngetimphawu letisheshe tibekhona teku caphelisa labafanele kutsi baticaphele.
tgt: hambiswiritano, nhlangano lowu wu kumbetela leswa ku hafu ya vana lava nga na mfukuzana laha afrikadzonga a va fembiwi naswitsanana.

src: lenhlangano yesekela bantfwana nebantfu labasha labanamdlavuta noma tifo tengati letisongela imphilo kanye nemindeni yabo.
tgt: ku pfuna ku tiyisisa leswa ku mfukuzana yi voniwa hi xihatla lexi kotekaka, choc yi fambisa minongoloko yo lemukisa emigangeni, yi byela vatswari na vana hi mayelana na swikoweto swo lemukisa swa le kusunguleni leswi va faneleke ku swi xiyaxiya.

src: "sihlose kusheshe sisi bone lesifo bese siselapha ngemphumelelo.
tgt: fawundexini leyi yi seketela vana na vakondloandzidyi lava nga na mfukuzana kumbe mipfilungano ya ngati leyi xungetaka vutomi xikan’we na mindyangu ya vona.

src: nanoma ngunini, ichoc ingana kekela bantfwana nebantfu labasha labangetulu kwalaba1 500, ibe futsi yesekela ngekwetengcondvo nangekwetenhlalo imindeni lengetulu kwale1 500," kusho seegers.
tgt: "hi na xikongomelo xo antswisa ku yi thumba ka ha ri ekusunguleni na ku humelerisa vutshunguri lebyi tirhaka hi ku hetiseka.

src: kulomnyakatimali lophe lile, seegers utsi ichoc yakhona kutfula tinsita kubantfwana laba1 724, bantfu labasha laba553 kanye nebantfu labadzala laba2 232 ngetinhlelo tayo letingumgogodla.
tgt: eka nkarhi wun’wana wihi kumbe wihi, choc yi nga va na ku hundza 1 500 wa vana na vakondloandzidyi lava nga ehansi ka nhlayiso wa yona, loko yi ri karhi yi nyika nseketelo wa swa miehleketo na wa vanhu eka kuhundza 1 500 wa mindyangu," ku vula seegers.

src: "tinsita tetfu tifaka ekhatsi kwesekelwa ngekwemiva ngesikhatsi basesebukene namdlavuta, kudvudvutwa, kunakekelwa kwaseku pheleni kwemphilo kanye nekwesekelwa uma sewu shonelwe," kusho seegers.
tgt: eka lembeximali leri nga hundza, seegers u vula leswaku choc yi kote ku nyika vukorhokeri eka vana va 1 724, vakondloandzidyi va 553 na 2 232 wa vanhu lavakulu hi ku tirhisa mino ngolokokulu ya yona.

src: timphawu tast siluan tamdlavuta wasebuntfwaneni s – funa lusito lwetekwe lashwa kusenesikhatsi lwetinkhomba letichube kako.
tgt: "vukorhokeri bya hina byi katsa nseketelo wa mati twelo eka rendzo ra vona ra mfukuzana, ku chaveleleka, nhlayiso wa makumu ya vutomi, na nseketelo wa loko va loveriwile," ku vula seegers.

src: isanral inikete tinkhontileka letintsatfu kulekota leyengcile yemnyaka we2021 umsebenti wacala kwentiwa emkhatsini kwabhimbi dvwane namabasa.

src: tincenye letitfutfukiswako nyalo sigaba semgwaco lomakhi lomitha (km) la19 losuka ecato ridge ufike edarda nelles, lowatiwa ngekutsi ngumgwaco iumlaas; sigaba semgwaco lesi20.6 km losuka edardanelles inter change kuya elynnfield park; kanye nesigaba semgwaco lesi30km losuka elynnfield park uye eashburton inter change.
tgt: swiyenge leswi nga eku ndlandlamuxiweni sweswi i 19 wa tikhilomitara (km) ku suka ecato ridge ku ya edardanelles, laha ku tivekaka ngopfu tanihi umlaas road; xiyenge xa 26.6 km ku suka dardanelles interchange ku ya lynnfield park; na 30 km ku suka lynnfield park ku ya ashburton interchange.

src: matekane utsi isip2 itawukhulisa lomgwaco weti gitjelwa newetekutfutswa kwemphahla losemkhatsini kwemahabhu etimboni la mcoka aseningizimu afrika, itawutfutfukisa kufinyelela kutinsita tekuhanjiswa nekunge niswa kwemphahla letisethekwini futsi itawu khuphula lizinga lekusebenta ngendlela lekahle kule phaseji.
tgt: matekane u hlamusela leswaku sip2 yi ta tiyisa logisitiki na phaseji ya vutleketli exikarhi ka mihlaluko ya le swivindzini swa mabindzu ya vumaki swa afrikadzonga, yi ta atswisa ku fikeleriwa ka switirhisiwa swo humesa no nghenisa swixavisiwa edurban no kurisa matirhelo ya kahle ya leka phasejini ya vutleketli.

src: ungete ngekutsi lomklamo uyincenye yeluhlelo lwavelonkhe lwentfu tfuko lwemnyaka we2030 neluhlelo lolukhulu letekutfutsa lwemnyaka we2050 futsi usekela luhlelo lwahulumende lwekwakha kabusha nele kuvuselela umnotfo.
tgt: u engetela leswaku phurojeke i xiphemu xa kungu ra nhluvukiso ra rixaka ra 2030 na kungu ra vutleketli bya xiyimo xa le henhla ra rixaka ra 2050 no seketela kungu ra mfumo ra ku aka ikhonomi hi vuntshwa na ku yi vuyelerisa eka xiyimo xa kahle.

src: kute kube ngunyalo, hulumende uhlose kutfu tfukisa luhlelo lwetekutfutsa lolutawuhambisana neti dzinga tangemphela tebantfu labahlala eni ngizimu afrika futsi lutawu bonelela bantfu labanemali lencane lebayisebentisela kukhokhela tindleko teku hamba.
tgt: ku ta fika sweswi, mfumo wu kunguhata ku hluvukisa sisiteme ya vutleketi lebyi nga kotaka ku yiseka emahlweni ku ya hi swilaveko swa xiviri swa vanhu lava tshamaka eafrikadzonga no korhokela vanhu lava nga na mali yintsongo leyi va nga yi tirhisaka ku fambafamba.

src: matekane utsi lokutfu tfukiswa kwalomgwaco kutawutsatsa iminyaka lesemkhatsini kwesi phohlongo ne10 kodvwa kuvalwa kwemigwaco kutawugcinwa kusezingeni leliphasi.
tgt: matekane u vula leswaku ku ndlandlamuxa swi ta teka exikarhi ka nhungu na 10 ra malembe ku hela naswona ku pfariwa ka gondzo ku ta endliwa hi switsongo.

src: tjwala bungalimata imphilo yemntfwana wakho asengakatalwa vukuzenzele unnamed bomake labakhulelwe banemsebenti weku tivikela banganatsi tjwala ngoba bungabanga sifo lesitsikameta kukhula kwemntfwana.
tgt: xihoko xi nga onha rihanyo ra n’wana wa wena loyi a nga se velekiwaka vukuzenzele unnamed vavasati lava nga biha emirini va na vutihlamuleri byo ka va nga nwi hikuva xihoko xi nga vanga xiyimo lexi nga khumbaka makulelo ya n’wana.

src: loku kushiwo lisekela lendvuna yetekufutfukisa tenhlalo, hendrietta bogo panezulu, losandza kucala luhlelo lwekulwa nesifo i999 foetal alcohol spectrum disorder (ifasd).
tgt: leswi i ku ya hi xandla xa holobye wa ndzawulo ya nhluvukiso wa vaaki, hendrietta bogopanezulu, loyi sweswinyana a simekeke nongonoko wa vuyimeri bya 999 foetal alcohol spectrum disorder (fasd).

src: inhloso yalomkhankhaso kugcugcutela imimango kutsi isite kuvikela bantfwana lebasengakabelekwa ngekufundzisa bantfu, kakhulu bomake labasakhona kubeleka, mayelana nebu ngoti bekunatsa tjwala ube ukhulelwe noma usamu nyisa.
tgt: xikongomelo xa pfhumba i ku hlohlotela vaaki ku pfuna ku sirhelela vana lava nga se velekiwaka hi ku dyondzisa vanhu, ngopfungopfu vavasati lava nga eka malembe yo bebula, mayelana na nghozi yo nwa xihoko loko va bihe emirini kumbe ku mamisa.

src: "kumcoka kutsi bonkhe bomake labakhulelwe nalabo labanesifiso sekutala bantfwana labaphile kahle bayekele kunatsa tjwala.
tgt: "swi na nkoka leswaku vavasati hinkwavo lava nga biha emirini na lava navelaka ku kuma vana lava nga na rihanyo ra kahle va papalata xihoko.

src: umonakalo lobangwa yifasd uba wemphilo yonkhe futsi awubuyiseleki emuva, futsi bantfwana labatalwa nalokugula baba netinkinga tasemtimbeni netasengco ndvweni," kwasho lisekela lendvuna bogopanezulu emcimbini wekwetfulwa kwaloluhlelo.
tgt: ku onha loku vangiwaka hi fasd i ka nkarhi hinkwawo naswona a ku lunghiseki, naswona vana lava velekiwaka va ri na xiyimo lexi va va na swiphiqo swa le mirini na swa miehleketo," ku vula xandla xa holobye, bogopanezulu eka ntirho wo simeka.

src: wangeta ngekutsi iningi zimu afrika yatiwa ngekuba nenkinga yekunatsa tjwala, lelive libalwa njengalamanye lamabi lahamba embili emhlabeni ngenca yemazinga alo ekunatsa tjwala.
tgt: u engeterile leswaku afrikadzonga yi tiveka hi ku va na xiphiqo xa manwelo, na tiko leri xaxametiwaka eka lamo biha emisaveni hi levhele ya rona ya manwelo ya xihoko.

src: lisekela lendvuna bogopanezulu usandza kuhambela tincenye letehlukahlukene talelive letfu, afundzisa bomake mayelana nebungoti bekunatsa tjwala bakhulelwe njengencenye yemkhankaso we999 fasd.
tgt: xandla xa holobye, bogopanezulu sweswinyana u endzerile tindhawu to hambanahambana ta tiko, a dyondzisa vavasati hi nghozi ya ku nwa xihoko loko munhu a bihe emirini tanihi xiphemu xa pfhumba ra 999 fasd.

src: lesikhatsi aseboitekong erustenburg enyakatfo nshonalanga, watjela takhamuti kutsi lizinga leku setjentiswa kabi kwetjwala emalokishini liyesabeka.
tgt: loko a ri eboitekong, erustenburg enorth west, u byerile vatshami va kona leswaku xiyimo xa manwelo yo biha ya xihoko emalokixini xa chavisa.

src: make lonetinyanga letine akhulelwe lohlala eboite kong, basetsane tlalang (28), lobekahambele lomunye walemikhankaso, utse wayekela futsi wagcina ngci kunatsa emva kwekutfola kutsi ukhulelwe futsi watsi sewuhambela emaseshini asemtfolamphilo elwatiso newesikhatsi lesandvulela kubeleka.
tgt: wansati loyi a nga na tin’hweti ta mune a bihe emirini tlhelo mutshami wa le boitekong, basetsana tlalang (28), loyi a nga ya eka rin’wana ra mapfhumba, u vule leswaku u yimile kunwa xihoko hi ku hetiseka endzhaku ko tiva leswaku u bihe emirini naswona u vule leswaku u le ku yeni eka nkambelo wa loko munhu a bihe emirini na tisexini ta mahungu etliliniki.

src: uncusa labanye bomake labakhulelwe kutsi bayekele leso sikhatsi kunatsa tjwala nekusebentisa tidzakwamiva.
tgt: u komberile vavasati van’wana lava nga biha emirini ku tshika ku nwa xihoko no tirhisa swidzidziharisi hi xihatla.

src: umshikashika wekubuyisa ubuntfu eningizimu afrika vukuzenzele unnamed mhla ti12 inyoni 1977, ste phen bantfu biko washona agcinwe maphoyisa ejele lelatiwa ngepretoria central prison.
tgt: nkayakayo wo nyika afrikadzonga ku twi sisa vumunhu hi vuenti vukuzenzele unnamed hi ti 12 ndzati 1977, stephen bantu biko u lovele emahlwe ni ka maphorisa epretoria central prison.

src: sitfunti sebuntfu, leku simiso lesihamba embili kulobushoshovu bakhe bekubuyisa sitfunti semuntfu lomnyama, sacekelwa phasi.
tgt: ndzhuti wa vumunhu, misinya leyi nga nchumu wa nkoka eka vugi ngiriki bya yena bya lemukiso wa vantima, u aleriwile yona.

src: ngekwemagama emmeli wemndeni wakhe sir sydney kentridge, "kushona kwakhe bekubuhlungu kakhulu futsi bekayedvwa ashonela emethini lephasi esemendeni yelijele."
tgt: hi marito ya qgweta ra ndyangu, sir sydney kentri dge, ra yena a ku ri "rifu ro vava no lova a ri yexe eme tseni ehenhla ka fuloro ya ribye endzeni ka sele ya khotso".

src: kutawuhlala kuyintfo lebanga lusizi lolukhulu emva kwayo yonkhe leminyaka leyengcile, kukhumbula kutsi steve biko bakaneminyaka le30 kuphela uma ashona.
tgt: ri tshama ri ri karhi ri vanga gome lerikulu endzhaku ka malembe lama hinkwawo ku tsundzuka leswaku steve biko a ri na 30 wa malembe ntsena loko a lova.

src: wabulawa asengakafiki esicongweni semphilo yakhe ngilabo bebasaba emandla ekubona imibono yakhe lesetulu yekutikhulula kanye nemitamo yekufaka kumuntfu lomnyama kutitsandza nekuba nesitfunti emadvodzeni nakubomake besive lesinsundvu.
tgt: u dlayi wile swa xitshuketani a ha ri ntsongo hi lava a va chava matimba na ntikelo wa mavonelo ya yena ya ku tintshuxa na matshalatshala ya yena yo tata vavanuna na vavasati va vantima hi vutinyungubyisi na ndzhuti wa vumunhu.

src: azange akhone kubona ekuphileni kwakhe loko lokubitwa ngekutsi ‘ngumklomelo lokhatimu lako", lekukubona buntfu bangemphela.
tgt: eka nkarhi wa vutomi bya yena, a nga kalanga a kota ku vona leswi a swi vula ‘xivandla lexi vanhu vo tala va xilavaka’, ku lemuka vumunhu bya ntiyiso.

src: abhala ngalomcondvo, kwadvuma kutsi watsi: "ngekuhamba kwesikhatsi sitawukhona kupha iningizimu afrika sipho lesikhulu kunato tonkhe – kukhulisa sitfunti sebuntfu."
tgt: ku tsala hi mavonelo lama, u vurile leswi a tivekaka hi swona a ku: hi ku famba ka nkarhi hi ta kota ku nyika afrikadzonga nyiko leyikulu leyi kotekaka ku twisisa vumunhu hi vuenti.

src: uma sincoba sitfola inkhu luleko yetfu ngemnyaka we1994, besivisisa kutsi lilungelo lekuvota liyincenye leyodvwa yemzabalazo wetfu wekutfola sitfunti sebuntfu.
tgt: "loko hi kuma ntshuxeko wa hina hi 1994, hi swi twisisile leswaka mfanelo yo vhota a ku ri xin’wana xa swiphemu swa hina swo kayakayela ndzhuti wa vumunhu.

src: eminyakeni lemashumi lamabili nesiphohlongo singene kuntsandvoye linyenti, sihlangabetene netinseyeya letinyenti, letifana nebuphuya, kuswelakala kwemisebenti nekungalingani.
tgt: makumembirhinhungu wa malembe hi ri eka xidemokirasi, hi hlanganile na mitlhontlho yo tala, yo fana na vusweti, ku pfumaleka ka mitirho na ku pfumaleka ka ndzingano.

src: ngenca yaloko, sivamise kunga boni kutsi sisuka khashane kanganani kute sikhone kufeza timiso letisisekelo semtsetfosisekelo wetfu futsi letichumanisa imicondvo netifundziso tasteve biko.
tgt: hikwalaho ka sweswo, hi tala ku hluleka ku vona leswaku hi fike kwihi eka ku tirhisa misinya leyi vumbiwa ra hina ri simekiweke ehenhla ka yona naswona leswi a swi tshama swi ri eka miehleko na tidyondzo ta steve biko.

src: ngemnyaka we1997, umbuso lobewungenalu velo wabulala lomunye umholi walelive lakitsi lobekatse mbisa kakhulu ngekumncisha kudla, emanti kanye nekwelashwa lobe kakudzinga kakhulu ngenca yekushaywa kabuhlungu ngemaphoyisa elubandlu lulo.
tgt: hi 1977, mfumo wo pfumala ntwela vusiwana wu dlayile un’wana wa varhangeri va tiko ra hina lava a va tshembisa hi ku n’wi tsona swakudya, mati na vutshu nguri lebyi a byi lava hi xihatla hi xivangelo xo mbeyeteriwa hi tihanyi hi maphorisa ya mfumo wa xihlawuhlawu.

src: emva kweminyaka lemashumi lamabili, sincumo senkantolo semnyaka we1997, inkantolo yemtsetfosisekelo yatsi kuphumelelisa emalungelo lasisekelo awo wonkhe umuntfu nekutfola ema lungelo abo etemnotfo kuluphawu lwemmango wentsandvoyelinyenti loluhlose kubuyisela sitfunti lesilahlekile.
tgt: endzhaku ka makume mbirhi wa malembe, eka vuahluri bya 1997, khoto ya vumbiwa yi vule leswaku ku fikelela timfanelo ta nkoka ta muakatiko un’wana na un’wana no lwela ku fikelela timfanelo ta yena ta ikhonomi i mfungho wa vaaki va xidemokirasi lowu ringetaka ku vuyisa ndzhuti wa vumunhu lowu lahlekeke.

src: namuhla eningizimu afrika, siyachubeka kuse bentela kuphumelelisa emalungelo lasisekelo awo wonkhe umuntfu waseningizimu afrika kute baphile imphilo lesezingeni lenge nato tifo, indlala nekuswela.
tgt: eafrikadzonga, eka nkarhi wa sweswi, hi ya emahlweni hi tirha ku fikelela timfanelo ta masungulo ta muafrikadzonga un’wana na un’wana ku endlela leswaku va ta hanya vutomi bya xiyimo xa le henhla byo pfumala vuvabyi, ndlala na ku kayivela swilo leswi va faneleke ku swi kuma.

src: imibuso yentsandvoye linyenti lelandzelanako isebentise imitsetfomigomo leletsa sitfunti sebantfu balelive lebesilahlekile ngekubanika imfundvo, kunakekelwa kwetemphilo, tindlu kanye netinsita letisi sekelo.
tgt: vulawuri bya xidimokirasi byo landzelelana byi tirhisile tipholisi ku vuyisa ndzhuti wa vumunhu lowu lahlekeke wa vanhu vo tala va tiko leri hi ku nyika dyondzo, nhlayiso wa rihanyo, tindlu na vukorho keri bya nkoka.

src: namuhla eningizimu afrika, kutfola imfundvo lesezingeni kulilungelo lelisisekelo.
tgt: eafrikadzonga, eka nkarhi wa sweswi, dyondzo ya kahle i mfanelo ya nkoka.

src: hulumende utjale timali kumfundvo legcile ekukhuliseni kahle bantfwana, ekusekeleni imiphumela yetifundvo ebantfwaneni balelive lakitsi labasesebancane, futsi kusita ummango ngeluhlelo leku phakela bantfwana kudla etikolweni kucinisekisa kutsi bafundzi labasesebancane batfola imiphumela lesetulu.
tgt: mfumo wu vekisa eka nhluvukiso wa vana lavantsongo, hi ku seketela mivuyelo ya dyondzo ya vaakatiko lavantsongo, no nyika xintshuxo hi minongonoko yo phaka swakudya eswikolweni ku tiyisisa leswaku vandyondzi lavantsongo va fikelela mivuyelo leyi kotekaka.

src: ngalesikimu savelonkhe selusito lwetimali kuba fundzi nangaletinye tinhlobo telusito lwahulumende, tinkhulungwane tebantfu labasha baseningizimu afrika labavela eminde nini lephuyile bakhonile kuba bodokotela, bammeli, bothishela, bososayensi, emaathizeni nabosomabhi zinisi.
tgt: hi xikimi xa mpfuneto wa swa timali xa swichudeni xa rixaka na swipfuno swin’wana swo hambanahambana swa mfumo, magidigidi ya vantshwa va afrikadzonga ku suka eka mindyangu leyi nga na vusiwana va swi kotile ku va madokodela, maqgwetai, va dyondzisi, vativi va sayense, vatshuri na van’wamabindzu.

src: hulumende usekela takhamuti letibutsakatsaka ngekusebentisa tinhlelo tekusita emakhaya laphuyile futsi iniketa ematfuba emisebenti ngaletinhlelo tahulumende tekucasha bantfu labanengi.
tgt: mfumo wu seketela vaaka tiko va swisiwana na lava nga sirhelelekangiki hi mpfuneto wo hlayisa no antswisa vutomi bya vaaki lowu engeteleriweke no nyika swivandlanene swa mitirho hi ku tirhisa minongonoko yotala ya ku thoriwa ka vanhu.

src: kuleningizimu afrika lebeyicindzetela leyabulala steve biko, bekute kukhu luma ngekukhululeka kantsi kuba sishoshovi kutepolitiki bekuholela ekutseni uboshwe ngaphandle kwekushushiswa noma ubulawe.
tgt: eka afrikadzonga leyi a yi tshikeleriwile leyi steve biko a nga lova eka yona, ntshu nxeko wo vulavula a wu hungutiwile naswona vugi ngiriki bya swa tipoliti a byi vangela ku pfaleriwa kumbe swo tlula swona.

src: namuhla eningizimu afrika, bantfu labasha labaneminyaka lelingana naleyo bekanayo steve biko noma lemincane kunaleyo bahamba embili kutebu shoshovi betintfo leti sedvute nabo, futsi bayakhona kutihlela kahle ngekukhululeka ngaphandle kwekuhlukunyetwa noma kwekudzingiswa.
tgt: eafrikadzonga, eka nkarhi wa sweswi, vantshwa va malembe yo tani hi ya steve biko hambi lavantsongo nyana va le mahlweni ka vugi ngiriki byo lwela swilo leswi va khumbaka, naswona va swi kota ku kondletela handle ko xanisiwa kumbe ku hlongoriwa tikweni.

src: kukhu luma nekuhlanganyela ngekukhululeka, lilungelo lekubhikisha kanye nelilungelo lekulingana ngembi kwemtsetfo ku yalandzelwa kubo bonkhe bantfu.

src: luhlelo lwekunika bahlukunyetwa emandla lubuyisa litsemba owen mngadi luhlelo lasethohoya ndou lwekunika bahlu kunyetwa emandla (itvep) lufuna kubuyisa litsemba nekutitsemba kuluhlelo lwetebulungiswa ngekusebentisa tinyatselo talo letinemandla letihlose kusita labo labasindzile kuludlame lolumayelana netebulili (igbv) nasekudlwengulweni ngekubanika tinsita tetengco ndvo.
tgt: nongonoko wo nyika vaxanisiwa matimba wu vuyisela ntshembo owen mngadi thohoyandou victim empowerment programme (tvep) yi lwela ku vuyisela ntshembo na ku titshemba eka sisiteme ya vululami hi ku tirhisa migingiriko ya wona yo tika leyi kongomisiweke eka ku pfuna vaponi va madzolonga lama simekiweke eka rimbe wu (gbv) na ku pfinyiwa hi ku va nyika vukorhokeri bya swa miehleketo.

src: letvep leyacalwa elimpo po eminyakeni lema20 leye ngcile, isebentela etibhedlela itshilidzini nedonald fraser letingaphasi kwamasipala wasekhaya ithulamela.

src: libamba lemcondzisi waloluhlelo fhatuwani manthada utsi loluhlelo luhlose kufaka indlela yekubuka tintfo lengavumeli nakancane kutsi kube nekuhlukunyetwa ngekwemacansi, ngekwegbv kanye nekwebantfwana kuletakhamuti tasethohoyandou, ngoba kuliciniso lelimsulwa kutsi loluhlobo lwemacala ayenteka kulendzawo.
tgt: mufambisi wa yona wo khomela, fhatuwani manthada, u vula leswaku nongonoko lowu wu kongomisa eka ku nghenisa vonelo ra ku nga tiyiseli ku xanisiwa hi swa masangu, gbv na ku xanisiwa ka vana eka vaaki va thoho yandou, loko hi languta mhaka ya leswaku milandzu leyi yi tele eka ndhawu liya.

src: utsi esikhatsini lesengci le, lubalobalo lwemacala beluvamise kukhomba kutsi bewamanengi emacala ekudlwengula ethohoyandou, kodvwa itvep ibe neligalelo lelikhulu ekuletseni lwatiso nekunika bantfu tinsita tekwelulekwa ngekuhlukumeteka kute kuliwe nalomkhuba lomubi.

src: njengoba umhlaba wonkhe utawube ubuke lomkhankhaso wetinsuku leti16 tebushoshovi bekucedza ludlame lolubhekiswe kubomake nasebantfwaneni kusuka mhla ti25 lweti kuya kumhla ti10 ingongoni, manthada utsi loluhlelo lunelisekile ngaloku leselikwentile lekukugcugcutela takhamuti kutsi tiwavisise emalungelo ato nekutsi tibike uma kwenteka emacala.
tgt: tanihi leswi misava yi nga ta va yi ri karhi yi languta pfhumba ra 16 wa masiku ya vutirheli bya ku nga vi na madzolonga eka vavasati na vana ku sukela hi ti25 hukuri ku fika hi ti10 n’wendzamhala, manthada u vula leswaku nongonoko wu enerisekile hi ku humelela loku endliweke hi ku hlohlotela vaaki ku twisisa timfanelo ta vona na ku vika vugevenga.

src: "letvep itfola bahlukunye twa beludlame lwasekhaya labasemkhatsini kwe80 ne100 njalo ngenyanga, bese kuba macala ekudlwengulwa la45 kuya ku50 labikwa njalo ngenyanga," kusho manthada.
tgt: "tvep yi amukela vaxanisiwa va madzolonga ya le mindyangwini va le xikarhi ka 80 na 100 n’hweti ni n’hweti, kasi ku vikiwa milandzu ya ku pfinyiwa ya 45 ku ya eka 50 n’hweti ni n’hweti," ku vula manthada.

src: sikhungo lesisodvwa lesiphetse konkhe kwalolu lelo siniketa tinsita letehluka hlukene kubahlukunye twa, letifaka ekhatsi lusito lwetemtsetfo, kuvikeleka kwebahlukunyetwa kulabo lababahlukumetako, kula ndzelela emacala lasenkantolo, kwelulekwa nekuniketwa emandla ngekusebentisa luhlelo lwekutfutfukisa emakhono, ngaloko bahlukunyetwa batfola litfuba lekucala kabusha.
tgt: tisenthara ta nongonoko leti nyikaka vukorhokeri byo hambanahambana eka vaxanisiwa, ku katsa na mfikelelo wa mpfuneto wa swa nawu, nsirhelelo wa vaxanisiwa eka vaendli va swiendlo, ku veka tihlo eka milandzu ya khoto, vutsundzuxi na ku nyikiwa matimba hi ku tirhisa nhluvukiso wa vuswikoti, hi ndlela yoleyo swi nyika vaxanisiwa masungulo lamantshwa.

src: manthada utsi letvep isebenta ngekubambisana nebetemisebenti yetemapho yisa aseningizimu afrika, litiko letemphilo kanye nelekutfutfukiswa kwemma ngo kute kuvikelwe kutsi bahlukunyetwa bangaphindzi bahlukumeteke kwesibili ngalesikhatsi bavula emacala.
tgt: manthada u vula leswaku tvep yi tirhisana swinene na vukorhokeri bya maphorisa ya afrikadzonga, ndzawulo ya rihanyo na ndzawulo ya nhluvukiso wa vanhu ku sivela ku vaviseka ka vumbirhi ka vaxanisiwa eka endlelo ro pfula nandzu.

src: "emacaleni ekudlwengula, basebenti betemphilo nema phoyisa beta etikhungweni tetvep kutosita bahlukunye twa bavule emacala bavulele labo lababahlukumetako futsi, babanika tinsita tekwelulekwa," usho njalo.
tgt: "eka milandzu yo pfinya, vatirhi va nhlayiso wa rihanyo na maphorisa va ta eka tisenthara ta tvep ku pfuna vaxanisiwa ku pfula milandzu ya vugevenga eka vaendli va swiendlo leswi na ku tlhela va nyika vukorhokeri bya vutsundzuxi," a vula tano.

src: kuvuliwe kufakwa kweticelo tensfas kwemnyaka we2023 vukuzenzele unnamed kuvuliwe kufakwa kweticelo kusikimu savelonkhe selusito lwetimali sebafundzi (insfas) semnyaka we2023.
tgt: swikombelo swa nsfas swa 2023 swi pfurile vukuzenzele unnamed nkarhi wo endla swi kombelo swa xikimi xa mpfuneto wa timali xa rixaka (nsfas) wa 2023 wu pfurile.

src: blade nzimande, usandza kwetfula lesimemetelo emhlanganweni webetindzaba.
tgt: holobye nzimande u vula leswaku xikimi lexi xi teke xiboho xo pfula nkarhi wo endla swikombelo ka ha ri na nkarhi, ku hambana na lembe leri nga hundza, leswaku ku ta nyikiwa lava nga ta endla swikombelo nkarhi lowu ringaneke wo yisa swikombelo swa vona na matsalwa yo seketela.

src: indvuna nzimande utsi lesikimu sincume kutsi kuvulwe lomjikeleto wekufaka ticelo ngembi kwesikhatsi, kute labo labatawufaka ticelo batfole sikhatsi lesanele sekutfumela ticelo tabo kanye nemadokhumenti lahambisana naleto ticelo.
tgt: loko a nyika xiviko xa mpfuxeto xa nkwama wa nsfas eka lembe ra dyondzo ra 2022, holobye nzimande u vula leswaku mpimanyeto wa r43 wa tibiliyoni wu nyikiwile eka xikimi lexi ku ya eka tihakelo ta tidyondzo ta vavu yeriwa, ku katsa na swakudya na mali yo famba, na switirhisiwa swo dyondza.

src: etfula umbiko lomayelana nekuniketwa kwetimali yensfas yemnyaka wekufundza we2022, indvuna nzimande utsi sabelomali lesitigidzigidzi letir43 sabelwa lesikimu kute sikhokhele tindleko tebafundzi tekufundza, letifaka ekhatsi sibonelelo sekudla nesetigitjelwa, kanye nesetinsita tekufundza.
tgt: u vula leswaku 985 672 wa swikombelo swi amukeriwile laha 140 636 wa swikombelo swi nga humelelangiki.

src: utsi batfola ticelo leti985 672 leti140 636 atange tiphumelele.
tgt: eka swikombelo leswi amukeriweke, 739 526 wa swikombelo swi pasisiwile swa xinkarhana ku kuma mali loko ka ha yimeriwe ku tsarisiwa eka swivandla swa dyondzo leswi faneleke.

src: kuleticelo lebatitfola, leti739 526 tavunywa kwesikhashana, kutawuya ngekutsi bafundzi babhalisile yini kutikhungo lebatikhetsile letehlukahlukene.
tgt: "[vunyingi bya] vaendli va swikombelo lava nga humelelangiki va tsandzekile ku nyika vumbhoni lebyi eneleke byo seketela swikombelo swa vona swa mali; ku tlula mpimo lowu vekiweke wa lava faneleke ku seketeriwa hi timali; se va fikelerile xiyimo xa le henhla xa vuthwaseri lebyi nsfas yi byi seketelaka hi timali na ku va va nga landzeleli tindlela ta dyondzo ta sekithara ya kholichi ya tvet," ku hlamusela holobye nzimande.

src: "linyenti lebafundzi lebafaka ticelo letingatange tiphumelele bahluleka kuletsa bufakazi lobanele lobusekela ticelo tabo tekutfola lusito; betingetulu kwalomkhawulo lobekiwe wekuvumeleka kutfola lolusito; nyalo labafundzi sevele baphumelele kutfola lizinga lelisetulu leticu letikhokhelwa yinsfas futsi bebangahambisani nalendlela yetifundvo temkhakha wemakolishi etvet," kuchaza indvuna nzimande.
tgt: hi ku ya hi mahungu lama nga eka webusayiti ya nsfas, ku sukela eka lembe ra dyondzo ra 2021, nsfas a ya ha nyiki mali ya tikhoso ta le ndzhaku ka tidyondzo ta le henhla.

src: ngekuya kwelwatiso lolukuwebhusayithi yensfas, kusuka kumnyaka wekufundza we2021, insfas ayisaniketi lusito lwetimali yetifundvo letentiwa emva kwekutfola ticu takho tekucala.
tgt: leswi swi katsa switifikheti swa le ndzhaku ka tidyondzo ta le henhla, tidiploma ta le ndzhaku ka tidyondzo ta le henhla, tidigiri ta tionasi, tidigiri ta timasitasi na ta phd.

tgt: leswi swi vula leswaku xiyimo xa le henhla xa vuthwaseri lexi xikimi xi xi seketelaka hi timali i digiri ya bachula.

src: kutfutfukisa luhlelo lwekufaka ticelokumitamo yekutfutfukisa loluhlelo lwayo kanye netinchubo tekwenta kube malula kulabo labanesifiso sekufaka ticelo, indvuna nzimande utsi kulomnyaka, insfas isebentise tindlela tekutfutfukisa loluhlelo kute kucinisekiswe kutsi konkhe kuhamba ngendlela lefanele.
